Class Element

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.app.osgrim.data.Element
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Building, Canton, Frequency, Incident, Level, Material, Nature, Service, ServiceCat, Space, SpaceCat, Team, User, Zone

    public class Element
extends java.lang.Object
    The class Element is the superclass of many classes in the data packages. All the classes that have an id and a name are the subclasses of Element.
    La classe Element est la superclasse de beaucoup de classes dans le paquet data. Toutes les classes qui ont un id et un nom sont des sous-classes de Element.
